"title": "7949: mission, of Israel",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7949",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God chose Israel to be his own people, and bring the good news of his salvation to the world. God's mission through Israel is fulfilled in the mission of his servant and continues through the mission of the church.</p>\n<h2>Israel as a channel of God's blessing</h2>\n<h3>Blessings for all people through Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:18\">GEN 18:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:2-Gen12:3\">GEN 12:2–12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:18\">GEN 22:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:4\">GEN 26:4</a> <em>God's promise repeated to Isaac</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:13-Gen28:14\">GEN 28:13–28:14</a> <em>God's promise repeated to Jacob</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:25\">ACT 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:8\">GAL 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Israel's call to be a nation of priests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:5–19:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:6\">ISA 61:6</a></p>\n<h2>God's desire to display his glory</h2>\n<h3>God's glory is to fill the earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:14\">HAB 2:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:21\">NUM 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:18-Ps72:19\">PSA 72:18–72:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:3\">ISA 6:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's people display his glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:1-Isa60:3\">ISA 60:1–60:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:13\">ISA 46:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:3\">ISA 49:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:5\">ISA 55:5</a></p>\n<h3>God's people declare his glory among the nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:3\">PSA 96:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:9\">PSA 57:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:10\">PSA 96:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps105:1-Ps105:2\">PSA 105:1–105:2</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:8-1Chr16:9\">1CH 16:8–16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:11-Ps145:12\">PSA 145:11–145:12</a></p>\n<h2>The nations will be drawn to God's people</h2>\n<h3>In recognition of God's presence among his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:20-Zech8:23\">ZEC 8:20–8:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:1\">1KI 10:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:1\">2CH 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:14\">ISA 45:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:19\">JER 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:27-Ezek37:28\">EZK 37:27–37:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:7\">EZK 39:7</a></p>\n<h3>To Jerusalem as the centre of universal worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:2-Isa2:4\">ISA 2:2–2:4</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic4:1-Mic4:3\">MIC 4:1–4:3</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:9\">ISA 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:6-Isa25:8\">ISA 25:6–25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa27:13\">ISA 27:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:6-Isa56:8\">ISA 56:6–56:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:16\">ZEC 14:16</a></p>\n<h2>God made known through his mighty acts</h2>\n<h3>God's deliverance of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:5\">EXO 7:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps98:1-Ps98:3\">PSA 98:1–98:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:15-Ps102:16\">PSA 102:15–102:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:26\">ISA 49:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:23\">EZK 38:23</a></p>\n<h3>God's action on behalf of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:10\">EXO 34:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:19\">EXO 8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh4:24\">JOS 4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:41-1Kgs8:43\">1KI 8:41–8:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:32-2Chr6:33\">2CH 6:32–6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps67:1-Ps67:4\">PSA 67:1–67:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:2\">PSA 126:2</a></p>\n<h3>God's renewal of Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:23\">EZK 36:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:40-Ezek20:41\">EZK 20:40–20:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:24-Ezek28:25\">EZK 28:24–28:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:16\">EZK 38:16</a></p>\n<h2>Israel as a witness to other nations</h2>\n<h3>God's people sent to other nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:19\">ISA 66:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:9\">1KI 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:2\">JON 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:2\">JON 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:15\">MAT 23:15</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of God's people bearing witness to him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:16\">GEN 41:16</a> <em>Joseph</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:16-Exod7:17\">EXO 7:16–7:17</a> <em>Moses and Aaron</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:3\">2KI 5:3</a> <em>Naaman's servant girl</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:44-Dan2:47\">DAN 2:44–2:47</a> <em>Daniel</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:16-Dan3:18\">DAN 3:16–3:18</a> <em>Shadrach, Meshach and Abednego</em></p>\n<h2>Israel's failure in mission</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:18\">ISA 26:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:20-Ezek36:21\">EZK 36:20–36:21</a></p>\n<h2>The fulfilment of God's mission through Israel</h2>\n<h3>The mission of God's Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:10\">ISA 11:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:12\">ROM 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:17\">PSA 72:17</a> <em>God's promise to Abraham is fulfilled through the Messianic king</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:16\">GAL 3:16</a></p>\n<h3>The mission of God's servant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:6\">ISA 49:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1-Isa42:6\">ISA 42:1–42:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:15\">ISA 52:15</a></p>\n<h3>The mission of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:9\">1PE 2:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a></p>",
